A world so colourful and real where you can literally touch, feel and become a part of the stories you see, a world of high definition. This perfect place of entertainment is called, Bollywood HD, a channel which offers treats from the worlds biggest producer of movies, Bollywood, all at your fingertips, exclusively for you. Tune in to experience larger than life blockbusters stories every single day, all year around. This one stop starry shop not just offers hot and sizzling premieres every month, but also gives you an upclose & personal peak into the gossip and news on the lives of the glamour Bollywood celebrities. Catering to all age groups, it offers diverse content and strong engagement, making it a trusted choice for advertisers and viewers worldwide.

Chardikla Gurbaani TV, with the motto A Bliss to Humanity, is a 247 Free Sikh Devotional Channel available globally on various platforms. It features live telecasts from Takhat Sri Harimandir Ji Patna Sahib, Gurdwara Sri Bangla Sahib, and special broadcasts from North America. Dedicated to Sikh teachings, history, Katha, Kirtan, and Dhadhi shows, it spreads the message of Gurbani worldwide.
